15360.name: Guard Tower Stairs
description: Stairs lead up to an even taller guard tower here.  Mildew caused
by years of the damn island air covers the stone steps.  The smell of
urine and other more nasty odors permeate the very stone.  They must
not provide the guards with a privy.

15359.name: A gnoll guard~
description: The guard in front of you has an Iron Ring brand, just like the other guards you have seen on the Island. What is it with these guys?
15359.room_name: A gnoll guard with the Iron Ring brand is standing here, betting on something below.

15250.name: a skulker thug~
description: The human is standing against the back of the School of Obedience, watching for unwary people to pass by. Watch Out!
15250.room_name: A skulker thug stands here, trying to ambush you.

15251.name: an Iron Ring Guard~
description: These tough looking orcish guards are stopping you from entering the Halls of the Iron Ring. The only way you can get through here is as a slave trader.
15251.room_name: An orcish guard stands here, barring your entry.

15999.name: A tiny goblin wizard~
description:
A goblin of very small stature stands here.  He is different from
any goblin you have ever seen because he is completely white.  His
clothes made of the purest white silk adorn his tiny body structure in
ragged form.  All but his eyes, which are bright {Yyellow{C redefine your
knowledge of a goblin.  {x
15999.d_flags: D Is enveloped in {YGOLD{c suddenly, then his body shatters dispursing several coins onto the floor{x~
15999.room_name: A tiny goblin wizzard scurries about searching for gold in the corpses

15355.name: A Skull Island Bridge Guard~
description:
The gnoll standing here has a grim look on his face. He has orders not to move too far, but he
looks like he'll chase you down for the fun of it.  He wears a brand of the Iron Ring, meaning
he's yet another employed guard of one of the most powerful slavers in the city.
15355.room_name: A guard with the Iron Ring brand stands here by the bridge.
